Probably either from:<ref>{{R:OED Online|pos=''n.{{sup|2}}''|noformat=1|id=164446|date=March 2010}}</ref>

* {{der|en|frm|retranchement|t=defensive work}} (modern {{cog|fr|retranchement|t=entrenchment}}), from {{m|frm|re-|pos=prefix meaning ‘again, once more’}} + {{m|frm|tranche|t=trench}} + {{m|frm|-ment|pos=suffix forming {{glossary|noun}}s usually of an action or a state resulting from an action}}; or
